riting and humorous take on the absurdities of everyday life offer timeless pleasures.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAnti-AmericanismvFiction. 0aPeople with disabilitiesvFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aFoster, David William.40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/31777840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477317785423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781477317785/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK